(389,2025,25,485,'6','Senior Capstone Project','Ann Cannon',1,'DSC',NULL,'Students will continue work on the project identified in DSC 502 with their capstone advisor. The work will culminate in a paper and a public presentation.  In addition to consulting with their capstone advisor and the instructor of the course, students will spend class time presenting their progress to classmates, sharing and developing ideas, asking and answering questions, and overcoming difficulties arising in their research. No alternate grade option.','DSC 502','Writing Intensive'),
