(391,2025,150,700,'2','Vacation','Registrar Staff',0,'VAC',NULL,'Vacation blocks are open to seniors who are on track to complete 31 credits by block 8 of their senior year.  Non seniors must petition for permission to take fewer than 4 blocks per semester. If the student is on track to have 31 credits by the end of their senior year, the petition will be approved and the student will be registered for a vacation block. Otherwise, the student must explain in the petition how they will make up the missed credit.','',''),
